library(DBI)
library(RPostgres)
con <- DBI::dbConnect(
  RPostgres::Postgres(),
  dbname = Sys.getenv("dbname"),
  host = Sys.getenv("host"),
  port = Sys.getenv("port"),
  user = Sys.getenv("user"),
  password = Sys.getenv("password")
)
# dbDisconnect(con)
order_atts_cumsums_enhanced_pg <- tbl(con, "order_atts_cumsums_enhanced")
order_atts_cumsums_enhanced_pg
order_atts_cumsums_enhanced_pg %>% 
  filter((datetimemlls >= pbegin & datetimemlls <= pend) & (att == "BOVOL" | att == "SOVOL" | att == "BTVOL" | att == "STVOL") & price > 2145.0 & price < 2205.0) %>%
  mutate(pcolor = pmap(list(att, obplotno), function(att, obplotno) {
    pcolor(att, obplotno) %>% unlist()
    print(att)
    }))
